  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The vision for the RM-TF is to promote revenue mobilization in support of sustainable
development. The RM-TF will have an enhanced focus on intensified engagements in selected
countries, and support a larger number of more targeted reform programs. It will further integrate
new fiscal tools into TA, allow for the provision of advice in newly emerging areas of global priority
(international taxation and carbon taxes), and support the development of training activities that are
closely linked to technical assistance.</narrative>
  </description>
